tool.name: PrintMaps

param.name: map_number
param.dialogReference: Select from the list. Each entry in the list is from the DDP index layer in the CURRENT map document.

param.name: output_file
param.dialogReference: This is a template to be used to generate output file names. The selected map number will be appended to the filename (with spaces replaced by dashes.)

tool.summary:
Exports one or more taxmaps to files.

Uses the CURRENT map document, which means the tool only works if you run it within ArcMap with a valid map document open.
tool.usage:
Select one or more map numbesrs from the list by checking boxes or using "Select All".

Select a format.

Edit the output location.

Click OK.

The page layout will update in ArcMap, and a file will be generated for each page.
